66 private sealed class XsdAttributeEntry
67 {
68 public SchemaNames.Token Attribute;
69
70 public XsdBuildFunction BuildFunc;
71
72 public XsdAttributeEntry(SchemaNames.Token a, XsdBuildFunction build)
73 {
74 Attribute = a;
75 BuildFunc = build;
76 }
77 }

79 private sealed class XsdEntry
80 {
81 public SchemaNames.Token Name;
82
83 public State CurrentState;
84
85 public State[] NextStates;
86
87 public XsdAttributeEntry[] Attributes;
88
89 public XsdInitFunction InitFunc;
90
91 public XsdEndChildFunction EndChildFunc;
92
93 public bool ParseContent;
94
95 public XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token n, State state, State[] nextStates, XsdAttributeEntry[] attributes, XsdInitFunction init, XsdEndChildFunction end, bool parseContent)
96 {
97 Name = n;
98 CurrentState = state;
99 NextStates = nextStates;
100 Attributes = attributes;
101 InitFunc = init;
102 EndChildFunc = end;
103 ParseContent = parseContent;
104 }
105 }

107 private sealed class BuilderNamespaceManager : XmlNamespaceManager
108 {
109 private readonly XmlNamespaceManager _nsMgr;
110
111 private readonly XmlReader _reader;
112
113 public BuilderNamespaceManager(XmlNamespaceManager nsMgr, XmlReader reader)
114 {
115 _nsMgr = nsMgr;
116 _reader = reader;
117 }
118
119 public override string LookupNamespace(string prefix)
120 {
121 string text = _nsMgr.LookupNamespace(prefix);
122 if (text == null)
123 {
124 text = _reader.LookupNamespace(prefix);
125 }
126 return text;
127 }
128 }

610 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdMaxLength, State.MaxLength, s_annotatedSubelements, s_facetAttributes, InitFacet, null, parseContent: true),
611 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdEnumeration, State.Enumeration, s_annotatedSubelements, s_facetAttributes, InitFacet, null, parseContent: true),
612 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdPattern, State.Pattern, s_annotatedSubelements, s_facetAttributes, InitFacet, null, parseContent: true),
613 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdWhitespace, State.WhiteSpace, s_annotatedSubelements, s_facetAttributes, InitFacet, null, parseContent: true),
614 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdAppInfo, State.AppInfo, null, s_appinfoAttributes, InitAppinfo, EndAppinfo, parseContent: false),
615 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdDocumentation, State.Documentation, null, s_documentationAttributes, InitDocumentation, EndDocumentation, parseContent: false),
616 new XsdEntry(SchemaNames.Token.XsdRedefine, State.Redefine, s_redefineSubelements, s_redefineAttributes, InitRedefine, EndRedefine, parseContent: true)
617 };

735 internal XsdBuilder(XmlReader reader, XmlNamespaceManager curmgr, XmlSchema schema, XmlNameTable nameTable, SchemaNames schemaNames, ValidationEventHandler eventhandler)
736 {
737 _reader = reader;
738 _xso = (_schema = schema);
739 _namespaceManager = new BuilderNamespaceManager(curmgr, reader);
740 _validationEventHandler = eventhandler;
741 _nameTable = nameTable;
742 _schemaNames = schemaNames;
743 _stateHistory = new HWStack(10);
744 _currentEntry = s_schemaEntries[0];
745 _positionInfo = PositionInfo.GetPositionInfo(reader);
746 }
747
748 internal override bool ProcessElement(string prefix, string name, string ns)
749 {
750 XmlQualifiedName xmlQualifiedName = new XmlQualifiedName(name, ns);
751 if (GetNextState(xmlQualifiedName))
752 {
753 Push();
754 _xso = null;
755 _currentEntry.InitFunc(this, null);
756 RecordPosition();
757 return true;
758 }
759 if (!IsSkipableElement(xmlQualifiedName))
760 {
761 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_UnsupportedElement, xmlQualifiedName.ToString());
762 }
763 return false;
764 }
765
766 internal override void ProcessAttribute(string prefix, string name, string ns, string value)
767 {
768 XmlQualifiedName xmlQualifiedName = new XmlQualifiedName(name, ns);
769 if (_currentEntry.Attributes != null)
770 {
771 for (int i = 0; i < _currentEntry.Attributes.Length; i++)
772 {
773 XsdAttributeEntry xsdAttributeEntry = _currentEntry.Attributes[i];
774 if (_schemaNames.TokenToQName[(int)xsdAttributeEntry.Attribute].Equals(xmlQualifiedName))
775 {
776 try
777 {
778 xsdAttributeEntry.BuildFunc(this, value);
779 return;
780 }
781 catch (XmlSchemaException ex)
782 {
783 ex.SetSource(_reader.BaseURI, _positionInfo.LineNumber, _positionInfo.LinePosition);
784 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_InvalidXsdAttributeDatatypeValue, new string[2] { name, ex.Message }, XmlSeverityType.Error);
785 return;
786 }
787 }
788 }
789 }
790 if (ns != _schemaNames.NsXs && ns.Length != 0)
791 {
792 if (ns == _schemaNames.NsXmlNs)
793 {
794 if (_namespaces == null)
795 {
796 _namespaces = new List<XmlQualifiedName>();
797 }
798 _namespaces.Add(new XmlQualifiedName((name == _schemaNames.QnXmlNs.Name) ? string.Empty : name, value));
799 }
800 else
801 {
802 XmlAttribute xmlAttribute = new XmlAttribute(prefix, name, ns, _schema.Document);
803 xmlAttribute.Value = value;
804 _unhandledAttributes.Add(xmlAttribute);
805 }
806 }
807 else
808 {
809 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_UnsupportedAttribute, xmlQualifiedName.ToString());
810 }
811 }
812
813 internal override bool IsContentParsed()
814 {
815 return _currentEntry.ParseContent;
816 }
817
818 internal override void ProcessMarkup(XmlNode[] markup)
819 {
820 _markup = markup;
821 }
822
823 internal override void ProcessCData(string value)
824 {
825 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_TextNotAllowed, value);
826 }
827
828 internal override void StartChildren()
829 {
830 if (_xso != null)
831 {
832 if (_namespaces != null && _namespaces.Count > 0)
833 {
834 _xso.Namespaces = new XmlSerializerNamespaces(_namespaces);
835 _namespaces = null;
836 }
837 if (_unhandledAttributes.Count != 0)
838 {
839 _xso.SetUnhandledAttributes(_unhandledAttributes.ToArray());
840 _unhandledAttributes.Clear();
841 }
842 }
843 }
844
845 internal override void EndChildren()
846 {
847 if (_currentEntry.EndChildFunc != null)
848 {
849 _currentEntry.EndChildFunc(this);
850 }
851 Pop();
852 }
853
854 private void Push()
855 {
856 _stateHistory.Push();
857 _stateHistory[_stateHistory.Length - 1] = _currentEntry;
858 _containerStack.Push(GetContainer(_currentEntry.CurrentState));
859 _currentEntry = _nextEntry;
860 if (_currentEntry.Name != SchemaNames.Token.XsdAnnotation)
861 {
862 _hasChild = false;
863 }
864 }
865
866 private void Pop()
867 {
868 _currentEntry = (XsdEntry)_stateHistory.Pop();
869 SetContainer(_currentEntry.CurrentState, _containerStack.Pop());
870 _hasChild = true;
871 }

873 private XmlSchemaObject GetContainer(State state)
874 {
875 XmlSchemaObject result = null;
876 switch (state)
877 {
878 case State.Schema:
879 result = _schema;
880 break;
881 case State.Annotation:
882 result = _annotation;
883 break;
884 case State.Include:
885 result = _include;
886 break;
887 case State.Import:
888 result = _import;
889 break;
890 case State.Element:
891 result = _element;
892 break;
893 case State.Attribute:
894 result = _attribute;
895 break;
896 case State.AttributeGroup:
897 result = _attributeGroup;
898 break;
899 case State.AttributeGroupRef:
900 result = _attributeGroupRef;
901 break;
902 case State.AnyAttribute:
903 result = _anyAttribute;
904 break;
905 case State.Group:
906 result = _group;
907 break;
908 case State.GroupRef:
909 result = _groupRef;
910 break;
911 case State.All:
912 result = _all;
913 break;
914 case State.Choice:
915 result = _choice;
916 break;
917 case State.Sequence:
918 result = _sequence;
919 break;
920 case State.Any:
921 result = _anyElement;
922 break;
923 case State.Notation:
924 result = _notation;
925 break;
926 case State.SimpleType:
927 result = _simpleType;
928 break;
929 case State.ComplexType:
930 result = _complexType;
931 break;
932 case State.ComplexContent:
933 result = _complexContent;
934 break;
935 case State.ComplexContentExtension:
936 result = _complexContentExtension;
937 break;
938 case State.ComplexContentRestriction:
939 result = _complexContentRestriction;
940 break;
941 case State.SimpleContent:
942 result = _simpleContent;
943 break;
944 case State.SimpleContentExtension:
945 result = _simpleContentExtension;
946 break;
947 case State.SimpleContentRestriction:
948 result = _simpleContentRestriction;
949 break;
950 case State.SimpleTypeUnion:
951 result = _simpleTypeUnion;
952 break;
953 case State.SimpleTypeList:
954 result = _simpleTypeList;
955 break;
956 case State.SimpleTypeRestriction:
957 result = _simpleTypeRestriction;
958 break;
959 case State.Unique:
960 case State.Key:
961 case State.KeyRef:
962 result = _identityConstraint;
963 break;
964 case State.Selector:
965 case State.Field:
966 result = _xpath;
967 break;
968 case State.MinExclusive:
969 case State.MinInclusive:
970 case State.MaxExclusive:
971 case State.MaxInclusive:
972 case State.TotalDigits:
973 case State.FractionDigits:
974 case State.Length:
975 case State.MinLength:
976 case State.MaxLength:
977 case State.Enumeration:
978 case State.Pattern:
979 case State.WhiteSpace:
980 result = _facet;
981 break;
982 case State.AppInfo:
983 result = _appInfo;
984 break;
985 case State.Documentation:
986 result = _documentation;
987 break;
988 case State.Redefine:
989 result = _redefine;
990 break;
991 }
992 return result;
993 }

1111 break;

1346 private static void InitSimpleType(XsdBuilder builder, string value)
1347 {
1348 builder._xso = (builder._simpleType = new XmlSchemaSimpleType());
1349 switch (builder.ParentElement)
1350 {
1351 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSchema:
1352 builder._canIncludeImport = false;
1353 builder._schema.Items.Add(builder._simpleType);
1354 break;
1355 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdRedefine:
1356 builder._redefine.Items.Add(builder._simpleType);
1357 break;
1358 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdAttribute:
1359 if (builder._attribute.SchemaType != null)
1360 {
1361 builder.SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_DupXsdElement, "simpleType");
1362 }
1363 builder._attribute.SchemaType = builder._simpleType;
1364 break;
1365 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdElement:
1366 if (builder._element.SchemaType != null)
1367 {
1368 builder.SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_DupXsdElement, "simpleType");
1369 }
1370 if (builder._element.Constraints.Count != 0)
1371 {
1372 builder.SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_TypeAfterConstraints, null);
1373 }
1374 builder._element.SchemaType = builder._simpleType;
1375 break;
1376 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSimpleTypeList:
1377 if (builder._simpleTypeList.ItemType != null)
1378 {
1379 builder.SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_DupXsdElement, "simpleType");
1380 }
1381 builder._simpleTypeList.ItemType = builder._simpleType;
1382 break;
1383 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSimpleTypeRestriction:
1384 if (builder._simpleTypeRestriction.BaseType != null)
1385 {
1386 builder.SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_DupXsdElement, "simpleType");
1387 }
1388 builder._simpleTypeRestriction.BaseType = builder._simpleType;
1389 break;
1390 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSimpleContentRestriction:
1391 if (builder._simpleContentRestriction.BaseType != null)
1392 {

1816 break;

1819 break;

1987 private void AddAttribute(XmlSchemaObject value)
1988 {
1989 switch (ParentElement)
1990 {
1991 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdComplexType:
1992 if (_complexType.ContentModel != null)
1993 {
1994 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AttributeMutuallyExclusive, "attribute");
1995 }
1996 if (_complexType.AnyAttribute != null)
1997 {
1998 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AnyAttributeLastChild, null);
1999 }
2000 _complexType.Attributes.Add(value);
2001 break;
2002 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSimpleContentRestriction:
2003 if (_simpleContentRestriction.AnyAttribute != null)
2004 {
2005 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AnyAttributeLastChild, null);
2006 }
2007 _simpleContentRestriction.Attributes.Add(value);
2008 break;
2009 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSimpleContentExtension:
2010 if (_simpleContentExtension.AnyAttribute != null)
2011 {
2012 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AnyAttributeLastChild, null);
2013 }
2014 _simpleContentExtension.Attributes.Add(value);
2015 break;
2016 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdComplexContentExtension:
2017 if (_complexContentExtension.AnyAttribute != null)
2018 {
2019 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AnyAttributeLastChild, null);
2020 }
2021 _complexContentExtension.Attributes.Add(value);
2022 break;
2023 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdComplexContentRestriction:
2024 if (_complexContentRestriction.AnyAttribute != null)
2025 {
2026 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AnyAttributeLastChild, null);
2027 }
2028 _complexContentRestriction.Attributes.Add(value);
2029 break;
2030 case SchemaNames.Token.xsdAttributeGroup:
2031 if (_attributeGroup.AnyAttribute != null)
2032 {
2033 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_AnyAttributeLastChild, null);
2034 }
2035 _attributeGroup.Attributes.Add(value);
2036 break;
2037 }
2038 }
2039
2040 private void AddParticle(XmlSchemaParticle particle)
2041 {
2042 switch (ParentElement)
2043 {
2044 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdComplexType:
2045 if (_complexType.ContentModel != null || _complexType.Attributes.Count != 0 || _complexType.AnyAttribute != null || _complexType.Particle != null)
2046 {
2047 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_ComplexTypeContentModel, "complexType");
2048 }
2049 _complexType.Particle = particle;
2050 break;
2051 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdComplexContentExtension:
2052 if (_complexContentExtension.Particle != null || _complexContentExtension.Attributes.Count != 0 || _complexContentExtension.AnyAttribute != null)
2053 {
2054 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_ComplexContentContentModel, "ComplexContentExtension");
2055 }
2056 _complexContentExtension.Particle = particle;
2057 break;
2058 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdComplexContentRestriction:
2059 if (_complexContentRestriction.Particle != null || _complexContentRestriction.Attributes.Count != 0 || _complexContentRestriction.AnyAttribute != null)
2060 {
2061 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_ComplexContentContentModel, "ComplexContentExtension");
2062 }
2063 _complexContentRestriction.Particle = particle;
2064 break;
2065 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdGroup:
2066 if (_group.Particle != null)
2067 {
2068 SendValidationEvent(System.SR.Sch_DupGroupParticle, "particle");
2069 }
2070 _group.Particle = (XmlSchemaGroupBase)particle;
2071 break;
2072 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdChoice:
2073 case SchemaNames.Token.XsdSequence:
2074 ((XmlSchemaGroupBase)ParentContainer).Items.Add(particle);
2075 break;
2076 }
2077 }
2078
2079 private bool GetNextState(XmlQualifiedName qname)
2080 {
2081 if (_currentEntry.NextStates != null)
2082 {
2083 for (int i = 0; i < _currentEntry.NextStates.Length; i++)
2084 {
2085 int num = (int)_currentEntry.NextStates[i];
